data.description: This is the home that you have been waiting for!  4 bedroom, 2 full bathroom home has been well cared for. Hardwood floors, new kitchen and new bathroom are waiting for you here.  Main floor fireplace and basement fireplace are wood burning with beautiful brickwork.  Central Air will keep you cool on the dogs days of summer.  The backyard is fenced in with a pretty private setting.   Finished basement offers the 4th bedroom and the 2nd full bathroom.   All appliances are included in the sale, including the washer and dryer.  New roof, newer water heater, plumbing and electrical updates and more - see attached list of improvements.   Seller is also including a 1 year Home Warranty for buyer!  Great location - North Muskegon Schools, Bear Lake and Muskegon Lake all within walking distance
